Package eu.focusnet.app.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationHelper
    A helper class to retrieve application configuration and Android facilities.
    Constant
    Contains constants that are not class-specific.
    Constant.AppConfig
    Constants related to Application configuration
    Constant.Database
    Constants related to local SQLite database
    Constant.DataModelTypes
    Constants definining the different types being used within the application content definition.
    Constant.DataReference
    Constants defining the syntax for the different means of accessing data.
    Constant.Extra
    Extras for inter-activity/Fragment communication
    Constant.Navigation
    Constants related to the navigation system of our application.
    Constant.Networking
    Constants related to the networking infrastructure.
    Constant.SharedPreferences
    SharedPreferences contain basic information for logging in and starting the application when no network is available.
    Constant.Ui
    UI-related constants
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FocusBadTypeException
    This Exception is triggered when an unexpected type is encountered.
    FocusInternalErrorException
    An FocusInternalErrorException denotes a problem that should not happen if the logic of the application was correct.
    FocusMissingResourceException
    A FocusMissingResourceException is triggered when a resource cannot be retrieved when it should.
    FocusNotImplementedException
    FocusNotImplementedException is thrown when some code branch that has not been implemented is reached.
